UseCases

Class Instructor

  • java.lang.Object
    • UseCases.User
      • UseCases.Instructor

  • public class Instructor
extends User
    Instructor is a child of User, because it is a specific type of User. The Instructor makes use of a Set of Classes. The Set represents all the classes she teaches in. The instructor has the less interaction compared with the system compared to any other user.
    Version:
    November 17th, 2016
    Author:
    Ulises Martinez, Jorge Huerta, Christopher Tighe, Team Siki
